<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/cb49e91a2dee4a36a0237269a7af18fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">舞台剧导演高志森：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/f3f47aa9874c4b0fbb6edf2807fdd0b2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">资深电影人徐小明：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/2e48edf03ee34722b7bb68d8147ce5a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">汪明荃：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/a5b4d39a31a649fdb28787cb77bcd2eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">薛家燕：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/eaf749359fa143858f4ec050adc50ed1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">胡枫、罗兰：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/623017c23b9945e9b437433ac3093468.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">TVB视帝黎耀祥：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/2b509fcadd034fd6927e2ba556080229.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
