<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/447a7e3963ab45ddbeb3f9d6eef3a00f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">刘锡贤、黄夏蕙：</p>
