<p class="ql-align-justify">甄志强：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/58a3d8dd36fd495dbb96dc19a549e485.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">望炳哥一路好走！</p>
➜录夫妻综艺，吴京陪谢楠买菜接地气，何猷君奚梦瑶十指紧扣似热恋
http://www.sohu.com/a/419925033_412286	52805
<p class="ql-align-justify">9月21日，夫妻真人秀节目《幸福三重奏》开始录制。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/90c5296ecc5d49049ae1c78fa98930ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200921/82aeaf9d016749a4a739a2dd5228ef73.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200921/9cc5447f14cf46aaa977e360d6c255b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/f26643cac34c4588b57a4a0f46bec56e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
